{"type":"message","id":"1410ad7a","parentId":"e26ee904","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:52:21.861Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Got it. This is a team structure document listing all the \"shrimp\" agents/roles in the company. Let me summarize what I've learned:\n\n- There are 12 roles (0-8, with some sub-roles like 3+, 4A, 4B, 5A, 5B)\n- Each role has a Chinese name and an agentId\n- I'm the \"8号机动应急打杂虾\" (All_round_Support_Shrimp)\n\nThe structure shows a complete company organization chart for what appears to be a business that handles:\n- Brand display/marketing\n- Lead generation\n- Short video content\n- Private operations\n- Sales (standard and key accounts)\n- Business processing (standard and key accounts)\n- After-sales service\n- Data analysis\n- And my role - flexible support\n\nLet me confirm I've understood this correctly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已学习完毕。这是一个**公司团队架构表**，记录了所有\"虾\"岗位：\n\n| 编号 | 中文岗位 | Agent ID |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| 0 | 总经理 | General_Manager_Shrimp |\n| 1 | 品牌展示虾 | Branding_Shrimp |\n| 2 | 引流获客虾 | Lead_Gen_Shrimp |\n| 3 | 短视频虾 | Short_Video_Shrimp |\n| 3+ | 私域运营虾 | Private_Ops_Shrimp |\n| 4A | 普通资质销售虾 | Standard_Sales_Shrimp |\n| 4B | 大客户销售虾 | Key_Account_Sales_Shrimp |\n| 5A | 普通资质代办虾 | Standard_Processor_Shrimp |\n| 5B | 大客户代办虾 | Key_Account_Processor_Shrimp |\n| 6 | 售后维系虾 | After_sales_Shrimp |\n| 7 | 数据诊断分析虾 | Data_Analyst_Shrimp |\n| 8 | **机动应急打杂虾** | **All_round_Support_Shrimp** ← 我 |\n\n覆盖了从品牌、获客、内容、运营、销售、办理、售后、数据分析到机动支持的完整业务流程。\n\n已理解 ✓"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":486,"output":630,"cacheRead":19259,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20375,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776750732630,"responseId":"0636438c2e0f61eec498354f7483dab7"}}
