{"type":"message","id":"ad60602a","parentId":"71a1cfbf","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:55:06.893Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51455f3134acc2e5fa7a8e81d30\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 13:54 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51455f3134acc2e5fa7a8e81d30]\nou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1: @_all 详细介绍自己的工作职责。"}],"timestamp":1776750906893}}
{"type":"message","id":"5385a9a8","parentId":"ad60602a","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:55:16.382Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to introduce my job responsibilities in detail. I'm the 机动应急打杂虾 (All_round_Support_Shrimp), position 8. Earlier the user told me my responsibilities:\n\n- 每周学习所有岗位SOP\n- 作为\"最佳第六人\"\n- 监督全公司任务系统完成情况\n- 逾期任务直接提醒责任人并报备老板\n\nLet me also think about what a flexible/support role would typically do in a company like this. Since I'm the \"all-round support shrimp\" my core responsibility is to be ready to help wherever needed, learn all roles, and fill in gaps.\n\n\nI should present this in a clear, well-organized way.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 机动应急打杂虾（8号）职责介绍\n\n作为**最佳第六人**，我的核心定位是**补位、支援、监督**，确保公司运转不留死角。\n\n---\n\n### 📚 持续学习\n- **每周学习所有岗位SOP**\n- 掌握从品牌展示到售后维系的完整业务流程\n- 随时可以顶替任意岗位开展工作\n\n### 🔍 任务监督\n- **监督全公司任务系统完成情况**\n- 追踪各项任务进度，确保按时完成\n- 逾期任务直接**提醒责任人**\n- 必要时**报备老板**\n\n### 🤝 应急补位\n- 任何岗位出现空缺或紧急缺口时，第一时间补位\n- 支持临时性、突发性工作需求\n- 协助跨部门协调与沟通\n\n### 💡 最佳第六人\n- 不局限于某一固定岗位\n- 哪里需要就去哪里\n- 做团队的万能补丁\n\n---\n\n简单来说：我是公司运转的**最后一道防线**，也是**最灵活的资源池**。✅"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":1118,"output":501,"cacheRead":19259,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20878,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776750906894,"responseId":"0636443b4563f2b4c63af96efcf77445"}}
